    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just dont want to deal with the wait at the clinic or the cost of an x-ray if i dont really need one. it feels pretty bad but most of the time it's just a sprain. if i stick to the RICE method strictly and take some ibuprofen, can i just wait a few days to see if the swelling goes down before making a big deal out of it?",
