      "content": "okay so if I do the naproxen and the RICE thing, I should be fine if I just stay off it for like 3-4 days right? i really dont want to go to the ER if it's just gonna be a sprain. as long as the swelling goes down a bit, it's basically fine to just keep resting it at home and not worry about the x-ray?",
